{
  "text": "Considering all the above, it is often complex to determine a priori which genes are to be analyzed and a \"non-hypothesis-driven\" approach has been applied in large NGS studies [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
  "correct_citation": {
